ealth%20sector%2C%20prohibiting%20promotion%20of%20many%20health-related%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisements%20can%20generally%20be%20categorized%20as%20either%20deceptive%20%28always%20forbidden%29%20or%20non-deceptive.%20Non-deceptive%20advertisements%20include%20two%20sub-categories%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epromotional%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eattractive%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EContradictory%20rules%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestrictions%20on%20health-related%20advertising%20in%20Turkey%20are%20not%20clear%20though.%20In%20fact%2C%20provisions%20found%20in%20separate%20pieces%20of%20legislation%20and%20ethical%20rules%20arguably%20contradict%20each%20other.%20Viewed%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20the%20primary%20legislation%E2%80%99s%20wording%20seems%20to%20be%20narrower%20than%20the%20scope%20of%20information%20which%20secondary%20legislation%20considers%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Doctors%20are%20permitted%20to%20announce%20their%20clinic%2C%20working%20hours%20and%20specialties%2C%20but%20cannot%20make%20advertisements%20and%20announcements%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2024%2C%20Law%20No.%201219%3B%20Primary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Doctors%20and%20dentists%20are%20permitted%20to%20write%20their%20name%2C%20surname%2C%20address%2C%20specialty%2C%20academic%20title%20and%20examination%20times%2Fdays%20in%20newspapers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20platforms%20and%20on%20prescription%20papers%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%209%2C%20Medical%20Deontology%20Statement%3B%20Secondary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Doctors%20and%20dentists%20are%20prohibited%20from%20publishing%20thank%20you%20messages%20in%20newspapers%2C%20or%20via%20other%20means%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%208%2C%20Medical%20Deontology%20Statement%3B%20Secondary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Healthcare%20organizations%20cannot%20make%20promotions%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2029%281%29%2C%20Regulation%20on%20Private%20Healthcare%20Organizations%20which%20Provide%20Outpatient%20Diagnosis%20and%20Treatment%3B%20Secondary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Private%20hospitals%20can%20make%20promotions%20and%20provide%20information%20which%20improves%20and%20protects%20healthcare%2C%20as%20well%20as%20inform%20the%20community%20about%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20current%2Ffuture%20services.%20However%2C%20information%20which%20is%20misleading%2C%20exaggerated%20and%20not%20scientifically%20proven%20cannot%20be%20used%20for%20promotion%20and%20providing%20information%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2060%281%29%2C%20Regulation%20on%20Private%20Hospitals%3B%20Secondary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Private%20hospital%20websites%20can%20contain%20information%20about%20the%20services%20offered%20by%20health%20professionals%2C%20who%20have%20the%20relevant%20knowledge%20and%20experience.%20However%2C%20websites%20cannot%20include%20treatment%20information%20of%20any%20kind.%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2060%282%29%2C%20Regulation%20on%20Private%20Hospitals%3B%20Secondary%20legislation%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Ethical%20rules%20say%20doctors%20should%20not%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2011%2C%20Turkish%20Medical%20Association%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20Ethics%20Rules%3C%2Fem%3E%29%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Advertise%20while%20practicing%20their%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Use%20advertisements%20for%20commercial%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Give%20a%20commercial%20appearance%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Act%20in%20a%20misleading%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Cause%20panic%20among%20patients%20and%20create%20unfair%20competition%20among%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20legislative%20hierarchy%20principles%2C%20provisions%20contained%20in%20secondary%20legislation%20carry%20less%20weight%20than%20provisions%20in%20primary%20legislation.%20Therefore%2C%20reconciling%20the%20contradiction%20would%20appear%20to%20be%20easy%20in%20practice.%20However%2C%20to%20ensure%20clarity%2C%20the%20overall%20regime%20needs%20to%20be%20revised%20to%20ensure%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EPermitted%20advertisements%20for%20doctors%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20in%20Turkey%20are%20subject%20to%20the%20general%20advertising%20rules%20%28above%29.%20A%20further%20restriction%20arises%20from%20the%20Turkish%20Medical%20Association%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20Ethics%20Rules%2C%20which%20prohibits%20doctors%20from%20undertaking%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eattractive%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20advertisements%20for%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20difference%20between%20promotional%20and%20attractive%20advertisement%20is%20that%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20promotional%20advertisements%20represents%20the%20only%20method%20of%20informing%20potential%20consumers%20about%20the%20product%20or%20service.%20Promotional%20advertisement%20falls%20short%20of%20containing%20exaggerated%2C%20overly%20ambitious%2C%20incentives%20and%20appealing%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EPromotional%3C%2Fem%3E%26nbsp%3B%3Cem%3EAdvertisements%3C%2Fem%3E%26nbsp%3B%E2%80%93%20Permitted%20advertisements%2C%20involving%20promotion%20of%20a%20specific%20product%20or%20service%2C%20via%20general%20information%2C%20but%20avoiding%20exaggeration.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ecarried%20out%20the%20first%20operation%20in%20the%20country%20using%20this%20technique%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20provided%20she%20actually%20did%20perform%20the%20operation%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Turkey%20using%20that%20technique%20and%20this%20fact%20is%20verifiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EAttractive%20Advertisements%3C%2Fem%3E%26nbsp%3B%E2%80%93%20Prohibited%20advertisements%2C%20involving%20exaggerated%20praise%20or%20encouragement%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seductive%20elements%20of%20the%20product%20or%20service%2C%20although%20fall%20short%20of%20being%20deemed%20to%20manipulate%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20will.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20she%20is%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ethe%20country%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ethe%20world%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20leading%20specialist%20in%20a%20specific%20medical%20field%2C%20even%20if%20disproving%20such%20claim%20is%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EApplying%20the%20Restrictions%20in%20Practice%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopments%20in%20medical%20science%20have%20led%20to%20a%20wide%20variety%20and%20depth%20of%20sub-specialties%20emerging%2C%20at%20ever%20smaller%20degrees%20of%20distinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20doctors%20in%20Turkey%20are%20permitted%20to%20publish%20their%20qualifications%2C%20medical%20specialties%2C%20and%20contact%20information.%20Such%20information%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20potential%20patients%20to%20identify%20the%20most%20appropriate%20doctor%20for%20their%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20under%20a%20strict%20interpretation%20of%20provisions%20in%20secondary%20legislation%20%28as%20is%20usually%20adopted%20by%20Medical%20Chambers%20in%20cities%20across%20Turkey%2C%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20Turkish%20Medical%20Association%29%2C%20any%20information%20going%20beyond%20these%20limited%20items%20is%20technically%20prohibited%20in%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrimary%20legislation%20clearly%20states%20that%20doctors%20can%20make%20declarations%20about%20their%20expertise%2C%20but%20cannot%20make%20advertisements%20and%20announcements%20%28%3Cem%3EArticle%2024%2C%20Law%20No.%201219%3C%2Fem%3E%29.%20However%2C%20modern%20life%E2%80%99s%20ubiquitous%20electronic%20and%20mass%20media%20combine%20to%20mean%20that%20consumers%20receive%20a%20constant%20flow%20of%20information.%20Therefore%2C%20perhaps%20a%20more%20realistic%20interpretation%20of%20this%20legislative%20provision%20is%20that%20doctors%20can%20make%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epromotional%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20advertisements%2C%20provided%20the%20advertisements%20do%20not%20stray%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eattractive%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20classification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20current%20practices%2C%20regulators%20in%20Turkey%20have%20adopted%20inconsistent%20approaches%20to%20interpreting%20and%20applying%20the%20various%20provisions.%20The%20overall%20result%20is%20that%20the%20collective%20bans%20on%20certain%20types%20of%20advertising%20for%20doctors%20are%20not%20always%20implemented%20in%20practice%20by%20local%20Medical%20Chambers%20or%20the%20Turkish%20Medical%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20commercial%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20uncertain%20legislative%20framework%20and%20inconsistent%20enforcement%20have%20a%20dampening%20effect%20for%20innovation%20by%20private%20enterprises.%20These%20businesses%20become%20less%20willing%20to%20develop%20alternative%20business%20models%20or%20technology%2C%20since%20their%20efforts%20and%20investments%20may%20later%20be%20deemed%20to%20violate%20the%20legislative%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurkey%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20regulating%20health-related%20advertising%20has%20clearly%20not%20kept%20pace%20with%20developments%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20other%20legal%20systems%2C%20nor%20with%20wider%20technological%20and%20media%20advancements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspective%20patients%20demand%20tools%20to%20simplify%20their%20search%20for%20appropriate%20medical%20specialists.%20Counter%20intuitively%20though%2C%20the%20trend%20towards%20simplification%20requires%20prospective%20patients%20to%20have%20access%20to%20an%20increased%20volume%20and%20complexity%20of%20information%20about%20candidate%20medical%20professionals.%20Detailed%20information%20allows%20prospective%20patients%20to%20assess%20and%20compare%20medical%20professionals%2C%20to%20ultimately%20identify%20the%20most%20appropriate%20person%20for%20their%20purposes%2C%20based%20on%20whatever%20indicator%20the%20patient%20deems%20most%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20when%20comparing%20and%20selecting%20a%20doctor%20for%20a%20given%20procedure%2C%20a%20prospective%20patient%20might%20wish%20to%20know%20all%20of%20the%20candidate%20doctors%E2%80%99%20patient%20volumes%2C%20track%20records%20with%20that%20procedure%2C%20surgery%20mortality%20rate%2C%20average%20recovery%20times%2C%20or%20even%20review%20references%20from%20past%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20making%20such%20detailed%20information%20about%20health%20professionals%20publicly%20available%20in%20Turkey%20involves%20a%20range%20of%20logistical%20and%20regulatory%20compliance%20difficulties.%20Logistical%20difficulties%20will%20immediately%20arise%20in%20ensuring%20the%20information%20is%20accurate%20and%20up%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20notably%20though%2C%20complying%20with%20unclear%20and%20arguably%20contradictory%20advertising%20restrictions%20will%20complicate%20such%20a%20project%20and%20discourage%20investments.%20Without%20doubt%2C%20publicly%20disclosing%20detailed%20information%20about%20medical%20professionals%20will%20attract%20close%20attention%20from%20local%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20regulatory%20bodies%20should%20actively%20consider%20Turkey%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20regime%20for%20doctors%E2%80%99%20advertisements%2C%20in%20order%20to%20update%2C%20clarify%20and%20realign%20the%20substantive%20provisions%20to%20ensure%20they%20achieve%20their%20practical%20effects.%20Until%20this%20occurs%2C%20health%20consumers%20in%20Turkey%20will%20face%20challenges%20in%20consistently%20and%20reliably%20accessing%20the%20level%20of%20information%20they%20seek%20in%20this%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22ImageUr